      <title>尽管大幅加息，尼日利亚奈拉仍创历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-drops-to-fresh-record-low-despite-jumbo-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚的大幅加息未能阻止奈拉的下跌，这个西非国家的货币在官方市场上兑美元汇率跌至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-drops-to-fresh-record-low-despite-jumbo-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和菲律宾将加强经济联系以抵御中国风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-philippines-to-bolster-economic-ties-to-fend-off-china-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尼拉驻华盛顿特使表示，在中国利用其经济影响力进行“胁迫”的风险下，美国和菲律宾正在努力建立更紧密的贸易和投资关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-philippines-to-bolster-economic-ties-to-fend-off-china-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:39:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的日本首相志愿者将出席道德委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄将出席议会道德委员会，试图扭转执政党行贿丑闻的新一页，该丑闻在领导层投票前几个月削弱了他的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称马来西亚法院恢复前总理穆希丁的贪污指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/malaysian-court-reinstates-ex-pm-muhyiddin-s-graft-charges-star</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《星报》报道，马来西亚上诉法院恢复了前总理穆希丁·亚辛的四项滥用职权指控，这对这位反对派领导人构成了新的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/malaysian-court-reinstates-ex-pm-muhyiddin-s-graft-charges-star</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国交易陷入停滞，菲律宾将目光投向其他石油资源丰富的地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/philippines-eyeing-other-oil-rich-areas-as-china-deal-stalled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位能源官员表示，菲律宾正在努力勘探该国其他可能蕴藏丰富石油和天然气的地区，因为两国之间的紧张关系导致与北京就南海联合资源开发的谈判陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/philippines-eyeing-other-oil-rich-areas-as-china-deal-stalled</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行拒绝降息后刺激支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thailand-ramps-up-state-spending-after-pm-s-rate-cut-push-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着泰国央行拒绝紧急降息的呼吁，泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛正在采取措施增加国家支出和公共投资，以支撑东南亚第二大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thailand-ramps-up-state-spending-after-pm-s-rate-cut-push-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国机构警告气候措施可能引发社会动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/climate-measures-risk-sparking-social-unrest-german-agency-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国环境局局长表示，除非政界人士采取更多措施减轻碳价格上涨对低收入家庭的影响，否则欧盟的气候议程将面临广泛抵制的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/climate-measures-risk-sparking-social-unrest-german-agency-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
